{"tid":2398564,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇ching搭過嘉魯達航空？","createTime":"2021-02-07T11:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T04:01:32.000Z","uid":75637,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"383b3d6abc037eac5af14b02c72f5ad5c247b169","tid":2398564,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"完左疫情想去印尼潛水，見印尼其他航空公司（lion air, sriwijaya）都出過事好伏唔敢搭，咁想問吓印尼最大嗰間嘉魯達有冇巴打搭過？評價係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecde050cba17e0cf12fadc3caba06601fb5de787","tid":2398564,"uid":271250,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"Ching你老母，有巴打，絲打呢d咁好嘅詞唔用，係要用埋d香討垃圾用詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeca8b10fe991472083f13ad6b61eaf6132481d0","tid":2398564,"uid":75637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecde050cba17e0cf12fadc3caba06601fb5de787","tid":2398564,"uid":271250,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"Ching你老母，有巴打，絲打呢d咁好嘅詞唔用，係要用埋d香討垃圾用詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:08:04.000Z","msg":"係，下次記得用返巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfafce58802c69af752188de6a70049e18be397","tid":2398564,"uid":149599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"有細個返印尼搭過"},{"pid":"224bf0b28f01e09258812aec6b02bbab35b0d892","tid":2398564,"uid":261124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:37:48.000Z","msg":"巴打黎搞笑？無乜邊幾間航空公司無出過事，嘉魯達Air  Crash Investigation 都有做過<br />\n<br />\nWiki link都俾埋你<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%98%89%E9%B2%81%E8%BE%BE%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E5%2598%2589%25E9%25B2%2581%25E8%25BE%25BE%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%25BC%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOd%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=fdde6667\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E5%98%89%E9%B2%81%E8%BE%BE%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n事故與意外<br />\n<br />\n自從1950年，該航空公司經歷15宗空難事故與1宗劫機事件。<br />\n<br />\n1996年6月13日，從雅加達飛往日本福岡的嘉魯達印尼航空865號班機起飛時衝出跑道，三號引擎起火爆炸，導致3名乘客遇難，其他272名乘客及機組人員無恙。<br />\n1997年9月26日，從雅加達飛往棉蘭的152號班機，在機場外30公里的山上由於偏離航線導致墜毀，全機234人罹難。<br />\n2002年1月16日，從馬塔蘭飛往日惹的421號班機，因當時氣象雷達技術不佳導致班機誤入惡劣暴風雨內，造成雙發引擎失效，加上電池維護問題無法重新啟動引擎，最後在河道上迫降時墜毀，造成1人罹難。<br />\n2007年3月7日，從雅加達飛機往日惹的200號班機，在降落時衝出跑道並爆炸，導致21名乘客遇難，包括5名來自澳大利亞的新聞工作者。<br />\n2020年7月1日，610號班機在降落時衝出跑道，所幸無人受傷。"},{"pid":"8b913300ffac8b0d15add49891dec608cde15c3c","tid":2398564,"uid":271250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eeca8b10fe991472083f13ad6b61eaf6132481d0","tid":2398564,"uid":75637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecde050cba17e0cf12fadc3caba06601fb5de787","tid":2398564,"uid":271250,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"Ching你老母，有巴打，絲打呢d咁好嘅詞唔用，係要用埋d香討垃圾用詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:08:04.000Z","msg":"係，下次記得用返巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:46:54.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打捍衛本土文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893059162e7a364be2f613cc855602fa88418e9b","tid":2398564,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"Garuda ok<br />\n內陸廉航Citilink係garuda揸旗, 可以坐<br />\n<br />\n不過來回香港印尼<br />\n有得揀都係坐返國泰先"},{"pid":"6780a5da1246c2259ac6a4943633a53ccadd460d","tid":2398564,"uid":75637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"893059162e7a364be2f613cc855602fa88418e9b","tid":2398564,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:50:16.000Z","msg":"Garuda ok<br />\n內陸廉航Citilink係garu